vulnerabilities.description: The Oracle Access Manager  portion of Oracle Fusion Middleware (component: OpenSSO Agent) is vulnerable to remote code execution. Supported versions that are affected are 11.1.2.3.0, 12.2.1.3.0 and 12.2.1.4.0.
